      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "code": {
          "language": "plaintext",
          "showLineNumbers": false,
          "showMiniMap": false
        },
        "content": "## I-75 South Metro Express Lanes \u2014 scheduled reversible operation.\n\nMARDOT's barrier-separated reversible express lanes south of Atlanta flip direction on a daily schedule: open **northbound** for the AM inbound peak, **southbound** for the PM outbound peak, with an IN-TRANSITION barrier sweep between. The controller (cab-i75s-01) publishes each state change as a standard `LaneStateChanged` event over the same NATS pipeline as every other device \u2014 no lane-control-specific path. *(Schedule compressed here so a full reversal is visible during a short take.)*"
      }
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "grafana-clickhouse-datasource",
        "uid": "clickhouse-vikasa"
      },
      "description": "The direction the reversible lanes are currently open to, from the latest LaneStateChanged. Blue = northbound (AM inbound to Atlanta), orange = southbound (PM outbound), yellow = mid-reversal barrier sweep.",
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "color": {
            "mode": "fixed"
          },
          "mappings": [
            {
              "type": "value",
              "options": {
                "0": {
                  "text": "\u25b2  Open Northbound \u00b7 inbound to Atlanta",
                  "color": "blue",
                  "index": 0
                },
                "1": {
                  "text": "\u25bc  Open Southbound \u00b7 outbound from Atlanta",
                  "color": "orange",
                  "index": 1
                },
                "2": {
                  "text": "\u27f3  In transition \u00b7 barrier sweep",
                  "color": "yellow",
                  "index": 2
                }
              }
            }
          ]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "gridPos": {
        "h": 6,
        "w": 16,
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4
      },
      "id": 2,
      "options": {
        "colorMode": "background",
        "graphMode": "none",
        "justifyMode": "center",
        "reduceOptions": {
          "calcs": [
            "lastNotNull"
          ],
          "fields": "",
          "values": false
        },
        "textMode": "value",
        "wideLayout": true
      },
      "pluginVersion": "11.1.0",
      "targets": [
        {
          "datasource": {
            "type": "grafana-clickhouse-datasource",
            "uid": "clickhouse-vikasa"
          },
          "editorType": "sql",
          "format": 1,
          "queryType": "table",
          "rawSql": "SELECT CASE WHEN argMax(flow_state, ce_time) = 'LANE_FLOW_STATE_IN_TRANSITION' THEN 2 WHEN argMax(open_direction, ce_time) = 'TRAVEL_DIRECTION_NORTHBOUND' THEN 0 ELSE 1 END AS direction FROM vikasa_mardot.reversible_lane_state",
          "refId": "A"
        }
      ],
      "title": "Current open direction",
      "type": "stat"
    },
    {
      "datasource": {
        "type": "grafana-clickhouse-datasource",
